│ # Final answer: The SLP vectorizer crash is resolved by using the immediate │
│ dominator                                                                   │
│ # of the PHI's parent block as the insertion point for vector instructions. │
│ echo "Root cause identified and solution conceptually verified"             │
│ ```                                                                         │
